Package: origami
Type: Package
Title: Origami: a visualization tool enhancing radar plot visualizations for multivariate data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yiwen Lu, Jiayi Tong, Lisa D. Levine, Alex J. Sutton, David A. Asch, Christopher H. Schmid, Haitao Chu, Rui Duan, Yong Chen
Maintainer: yiwenlu <yiwenlu@sas.upenn.edu>
Description: Origami plot maintains the original functionality of a radar chart and avoids potential misuse of its connected regions, with newly added features to better assist multi-criteria decision-making.
Imports: fmsb, plotrix, grDevices
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
